title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 244: Featuring Jack Eichel
description:
On Thursday’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Buffalo Sabres superstar, Jack Eichel. Jack joins (56:34) to talk about this season in Buffalo, his new coach, Rasmus Dahlin and a bunch more. The guys also touch on a ton of NHL news, including Jay Bouwmeester, Shea Weber, the Jets and more. The boys also wrap up with a gambling corner (02:01:25) from RA.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
